{"tid":1119321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣咁諗過","createTime":"2019-04-21T22:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T04:44:42.000Z","uid":248406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d963752b3bf0a7d54fef897dcc1f44de71d1e1d0","tid":1119321,"uid":248406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T22:39:17.000Z","msg":"我係中學已經有咁諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想自己冇任何親戚<br />\n因為好似自己成世人做緊既野都係做比佢地睇<br />\n我覺得如果冇佢地既話 我自己唔會揀讀大學<br />\n覺得係香港唔讀大學都有權搵得多錢有前途<br />\n加上學費又貴 我又要自己還返 諗起都覺得慘<br />\n我會想早d返工 想自己搬出去 租間劏房住都好<br />\n之前諗諗下甚至有諗過扮失憶扮唔識佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係佢地對我唔好對我好多意見 我先有呢個諗法<br />\n而係覺得有種無形既壓力<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n親情L即管插 預咗<br />\n只係想知下咁諗係咪好痴線"},{"pid":"f54dc2dbbd2eb36a46eb52a968d1f00155b883e5","tid":1119321,"uid":37585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T22:59:38.000Z","msg":"中國人家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0017a4f69cf3438faffc343e309b9a1d838807","tid":1119321,"uid":248406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f54dc2dbbd2eb36a46eb52a968d1f00155b883e5","tid":1119321,"uid":37585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T22:59:38.000Z","msg":"中國人家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}